Packages
edu.utdallas.paged.assembler This package defines the use of assemblers to create various models used in this extension.
edu.utdallas.paged.db A general database backend for persistent storage of Jena models. This package allows retrieval of large datasets from a MySQL database.
edu.utdallas.paged.graph Defines the Graph in this extension.
edu.utdallas.paged.graph.query Defines the graph-level Query classes, allowing multi-pattern query over arbitrary graphs.
edu.utdallas.paged.mem.algorithm Defines the algorithms used for memory management of RDF graphs.
edu.utdallas.paged.mem.cache Defines various cache strategies used in memory management of RDF graphs.
edu.utdallas.paged.mem.disk Defines various query mechanisms for Lucene indicies.
edu.utdallas.paged.mem.util Miscellaneous collection of utility classes.
edu.utdallas.paged.query Defines the SPARQL query execution mechanisms over this extension.
edu.utdallas.paged.rdf.model A package for creating and manipulating RDF graphs with this extension.
edu.utdallas.paged.sdb A SPARQL database backend for persistent storage of Jena models. This package allows retrieval of large datasets from a MySQL database.
edu.utdallas.paged.sdb.graph Defines the Graph classes for the SPARQL database model in this extension.
edu.utdallas.paged.shared.impl This package defines the properties that can be specified as user parameters in this extension.
